        <title>Setting up the project</title>
        <paragraph>In this short first part, we'll set up and organize the project.</paragraph>
        <paragraph>Launch Godot and create a new project.</paragraph>
        <image candidates="{'*': 'getting_started/first_2d_game/img/new-project-button.webp'}" original_uri="img/new-project-button.webp" uri="getting_started/first_2d_game/img/new-project-button.webp"></image>
        <paragraph>When creating the new project, you only need to choose a valid <emphasis>Project Path</emphasis>. You can leave the other default settings alone.</paragraph>
        <container classes="sphinx-tabs" type="tab-element">
