                    and <literal>fonts/</literal> directories to your project's directory.</paragraph>
            </div>
            <div aria-labelledby="tab-0-0-1" classes="sphinx-tabs-panel" hidden="true" ids="panel-0-0-1" name="0-1" role="tabpanel" tabindex="0">
